text: Sedilo (Sèdilo) is a town and comune (municipality) in the Province of Oristano in Sardinia, Italy. As of 2016, 2,122 people lived there. Its area is 68.45 km².Istituto nazionale di statistica - Superficie territoriale per zona altimetrica It is 283 meters above sea level. == References == == Other websites == Category:Communes of the Province of Oristano
